The keys in ./keys and the download URLs in salon.mjs come from
google-deepmind/tell_me_a_story (Apache-2.0), published there so that
people — not scrapers — can read the corpus. The dataset itself is
"Tell Me A Story" (Huot et al., Agents' Room, ICLR 2025), licensed
CC-BY 4.0. The decrypted corpus is deliberately untracked here: the
authors encrypted it to keep it out of automated scrapes, and this
house honors that. Attribution and citation live in
docs/research/AGENTS-ROOM.md.
